fields.description: Provides the display name of the app-specific resource represented by the app scope. Provided for display purposes since appScopeId is often an immutable, non-human-readable id. Read-only.
fields.name: DisplayName

fields.description: Describes the type of app-specific resource represented by the app scope and is provided for display purposes, so a user interface can convey to the user the kind of app specific resource represented by the app scope. Read-only.
fields.name: Type
